  <summary date="2021-05-06T20:01:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Nonalcoholic Steatohepatitis Care Act of 2020 or the NASH Care Act of 2020

This bill reauthorizes, establishes, or expands various grants, research, disease surveillance, and other efforts to prevent, diagnose, and treat nonalcoholic fatty liver disease and nonalcoholic steatohepatitis (i.e., liver inflammation and damage caused by a buildup of fat in the liver).</summary>
